		</RichText>
		<RichText x="67" y="736" width="138" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfbf">(N5) <span color="#ffffff">多元作战：</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="538" width="505" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">永劫龙兽会以自身生命值划分为4个周期进行战斗：由生命值处于<span color="#ffdfbf">75%/<br/>49%/24%</span><span>的瞬时锁血进行划分，每个周期内永劫龙兽会</span><span color="#ffdfbf">吸收周期内所受伤害最多的元素</span><span>进行转换并提升</span><span color="#ffbfbf">200%</span><span>对应抗性。<br/>触发瞬时锁血后，永劫龙兽会立即播放瘫痪动画，随后吸收元素。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<Rect x="576" y="32" width="768" height="768" alpha="1" d:userLabel="固定矩形" visible="false" blendMode="normal" radiusX="0" radiusY="0">
