		<RichText x="1538" y="320" width="444" height="151" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放「散落洪流」前，会立即吸收元素填充元素螺栓，使该次技能附上元素伤害，元素的种类以<span color="#ffebbf">上一周期</span><span>所受</span><span color="#ffbfbf">总和最高</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffecbf">伤害</span><span>为准</span><span color="#ffecbf">(物伤则无属性)</span><span>，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">不吸收附着的元素</span><span>。元素吸收完毕后该元素抗性</span><span color="#ffbfbf">+60%</span><span>，提升的抗性仅能通过吸收其他属性来转移。<br/>仅瘫痪动画期间不记录伤害。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>元素抗性提升效果变为</span><span color="#ffbfbf">200%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
